display="inline"><![CDATA[z_{0}\in \mathbb {C}]]></fr:tex> where <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[|f|]]></fr:tex> attains its minimum value in <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbb {R}]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
 
   
